                                    <div class="btn-code-block" data-lang="html" style="display:block"><div class="btn-code-header"><span>HTML</span><button onclick="copyInputCode(this)"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i></button></div><pre><code>&lt;div class="zc-input-field"&gt;
  &lt;div class="zc-input-wrapper zc-input-wrapper-success"&gt;
    &lt;input class="zc-input" type="text" value="john@example.com" /&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
