&lt;/div&gt;</code></pre></div>
                                    <div class="btn-code-block" data-lang="scss" style="display:none"><div class="btn-code-header"><span>SCSS</span><button onclick="copyInputCode(this)"><i class="fas fa-copy"></i></button></div><pre><code>.zc-input-wrapper-success {
